{"title_page": "Tamil Nadu", "text_new": "{{Short description|State in Southern India}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2020}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=October 2019}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n<!-- See template:Infobox settlement for additional fields and descriptions -->| name                            = Tamil Nadu\n| other_name                      = Tamilagam\n| native_name                     = <!-- Don't add Indic script here, per [[WP:INDICSCRIPT]] -->\n| image_skyline                   = {{Photomontage\n | photo1a      = The big temple.jpg\n | photo2a      = Shore Temple (16217100293).jpg\n | photo2b      = Sri Ranganathaswamy Temple, dedicated to Vishnu, in Srirangam, near Tiruchirappali (28) (37464519366).jpg\n | photo3a      = Thoothukudi Thermal Power Station at Night 1 crop (cropped).jpg\n | photo4a      = Hogenakkal_Falls_Close.jpg\n | photo4b      = Kanyakumari rock temple.jpg\n | spacing      = 1\n | size         = 250\n | position     = centre\n | border       = 0\n | color        = #000000\n | foot_montage = ''From top, left to right:''<br />[[Great Living Chola Temples]], [[Shore Temple]], [[Ranganathaswamy Temple, Srirangam|Ranganathaswamy Temple Srirangam]], [[Tuticorin Thermal Power Station|Thoothukudi Thermal Power Station]], [[Hogenakkal Falls]] and [[Vivekananda Rock Memorial]]\n }}\n| image_caption                   = \n| image_flag                      = \n| type                            = [[States and union territories of India|State of India]]\n| image_blank_emblem              = TamilNadu Logo.svg\n| blank_emblem_type               = [[Emblem of Tamil Nadu|Emblem]]\n| blank_emblem_size               = 100px\n| anthem                          = \"[[Tamil Thai Valthu]]\"{{ref|est|}}<br />''(Invocation to Mother Tamil)''\n| motto                           = <br>Vaymaiye Vellum<br>(''Truth alone triumphs'')\n| image_map                       = IN-TN.svg\n| map_alt                         = \n| map_caption                     = Location of Tami